; Hub — cleanup pass on Wave 2.
;   - Parallax skyline removed; the silhouette towers read as a
;     landscape and clashed with the cosmic Hub vibe. Only the nebula
;     far layer remains in the ParallaxBackground.
;   - A giant ornate clock joins the upper-right of the scene as the
;     new focal anchor. Hands sweep at sped-up but proportional rates
;     (minute 1 rev / 60s, hour 1 rev / 12min) via a single
;     AnimationPlayer with one 720s looping animation.
;   - Each door now uses a richer arch texture with a baked-in radial
;     void interior; the per-door spinning Void Sprite2D and its
;     VoidSpin AnimationPlayer are no longer needed and are removed.
;   - Fog band, fireflies, door bob animation, door collision /
;     interaction wiring, and Curiosity / TouchControls instances are
;     unchanged.
